title: Eddie Attempts To Kick A 30-yard Field Goal + What ONE thing we are most Thankful For + Bobby’s Mailbag: Do you need to tell Fiancé when you buy something Expensive?
itunes:title: Eddie Attempts To Kick A 30-yard Field Goal + What ONE thing we are most Thankful For + Bobby’s Mailbag: Do you need to tell Fiancé when you buy something Expensive?
description:
Eddie go out to the Titans Field to attempt to kick a 30-yard field goal. He had told Bobby that he could nail it no problem. If he makes it, he wins a pair of shoes for all of his kids from Bobby. If he fails, he has to shave 3 lines in his eyebrow and hold a sign that says “I am not an athlete”. We talk about the ONE thing we are most thankful for with Thanksgiving being tomorrow. Bobby opens up the mailbag with an email from a listener who needs advice on handle a situation with her fiancé about her spending habits. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
